it.polimi.se2018.model

Class RoundTrack

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2018.model.RoundTrack

  • public class RoundTrack
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the round track in the game.

    Its role is to keep track of all the dice that are left unused after each round, since they still may be used in some cases

    The class is immutable.

    Author:
    dvdmff

      • swap

        public Die swap(Coordinates coordinates,
                Die die)
        Exchanges the die at the specified coordinates with the given one. This method swaps two dice, one of which has to be among the leftovers and the other mustn't. If this isn't the case, the method returns false to indicate that the operation is not permitted.
        Parameters:
        coordinates - The location of the die to swap in the round track.
        die - The die to be inserted in the leftovers.
        Returns:
        A reference to the die that has been removed from the round track. A value of null indicates that the swap was unsuccessful.
